# 📊 Sales Dashboard using Power BI

## 📁 Project Overview

Developed an interactive Power BI dashboard to analyze business performance, focusing on sales trends, profitability, and customer behavior.

## 📊 Dashboard Features

* Summary tab with key KPIs (Revenue, Profit, Orders)
* Sales trend analysis over time
* Profit vs Revenue comparison
* Segment-wise performance analysis
* Detailed profitability analysis table
* Customer summary dashboard
* Identification of top customers based on order value

## 🧠 Key Insights

* Identified sales growth trends and seasonal patterns
* Compared profitability across different customer segments
* Detected high-value customers contributing significantly to revenue
* Analyzed customer purchasing behavior

## 🛠 Tools Used

* Power BI
* Power Query (for data transformation)

## 💡 Skills Demonstrated

* Data Visualization
* Dashboard Design
* Business Analysis
* Data Storytelling
